en layer with the\ndeveloping helium convection zone. It is very important to carefully consider\nthe bias from observational selection effects when drawing these conclusions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Sep 2015 09:18:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-04"}
